      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "所以取消分支是Processing → Cancelled → Retail_CustomerLoyalty，正向流程终点是Delivered → Retail_CouponSystem。这样画对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Processing",
